snippet.title: Great North Shelter 2 - Official Gameplay Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Great North Shelter 2 is a first-person mystery adventure with horror elements. This game will react to your actions: for example, if you try to go outside the map, you will press some button many times, and so on. There is humor, fear and many hidden details.

RELEASE DATE: Q2 2023

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2303160/Great_North_Shelter_2/
